@startuml phase7_interview
' State diagram: User selects company (status=interview) → load meta.json persona → Groq system prompt built → Interview chat starts → [user sends message] → Groq responds as HR/CEO → [Help Me clicked] → Groq pauses, returns coaching tip → [End session] → Groq scores 0-10 → save to interview_sessions/{id}/{session_id}.json → [Retry/Reset available]

[*] --> Setup
Setup : Load company persona
Setup : Build system prompt (HR/CEO)

Setup --> Chatting : start_session()

state Chatting {
    [*] --> AI_Turn
    AI_Turn : AI asks question
    AI_Turn --> User_Turn : wait_for_input
    
    User_Turn --> AI_Turn : send_message()
    User_Turn --> HelpRequested : click_help()
    
    HelpRequested --> User_Turn : show_coaching_tip()
}

Chatting --> Scoring : end_session()
Scoring : Groq scores performance (0-10)
Scoring : Save session to JSON

Scoring --> FinalState
FinalState : Display results
FinalState --> Setup : retry()
FinalState --> [*] : exit()
@enduml
